Noko , ɔlua kɛzi Mame Ritsuko yɛle me la ati , ɔmaanle membikyele ye kpalɛ .
Dapɛne biala , yɛkɔbɔ edwɛkpa ne nolo na yɛkɔ Kilisienema nyianu .
Ɔmaanle me nee ye nlonle tii , ɔrɛlɛle me aleɛ nee kaade na ɔhɛlɛle me ngɛlata fane dɔɔnwo .
Mame Ritsuko subane kpalɛ ne boale me . ”
Kaori mame wule la ɛvolɛ bulu nee nwiɔ ɛpɛ nu , na ɛnɛ ɔ nee ɔ hu ɛlɛfa bɛ mekɛ kɔsɔɔti abɔ edwɛkpa ne nolo .
Kaori ka kɛ , “ Mame Ritsuko kɔ zo dwenle me nwo .
Saa mekɔ sua nu a , mekpɔla ye dahuu na yɛdi adwelie mɔɔ maa anwosesebɛ . ”
Awie bieko mɔɔ ɔdaye noko ɔnyianle moalɛ la a le Poli , mɔɔ ɔle Gyihova Dasevolɛ wɔ Cyprus la .
Ɛnee Poli ahu Sozos , ati akunlu le kɛnlɛma mɔɔ yɛ neazo kpalɛ kɛ Kilisienenli neavolɛ ɔlua nrisa nee ahunlanvolɛ mɔɔ ɔmaa bɛba ye sua nu na ɔ nee bɛ bɔ nu di aleɛ la azo .
Ɔyɛ alɔbɔlɛ kɛ , mɔɔ Sozos nyianle ɛvolɛ 53 la , nyila mɔɔ nwu amelɛ ne anu la hunle ye .
Bɛbɔle ɔ bo kɛ bɛkɔ debiezukoalɛ wɔ Gyihova Alasevolɛ asafo bie anu .
Poli ka kɛ , “ Agɔnwolɛma mɔɔ wɔ me asafo fofolɛ ne anu la ɛnze mɔɔ ɛdo yɛ nee tɛnlabelɛ mɔɔ anu yɛ se mɔɔ yɛwɔ nu la anwo ɛhwee .
Noko , ɛhye anzi bɛ adenle kɛ bɛbabikye yɛ na bɛaha edwɛkɛ mɔɔ kyekye yɛ rɛle na ɔboa yɛ la .
Nea kɛzi moalɛ ɛhye rale wɔ mekɛ kpalɛ nu mɔɔ ɛnee me ra ne hyia ɔ ze anwo kpalɛ la !
Mgbanyima mɔɔ wɔ asafo ne anu la anye liele Daniel anwo .
Saa bɛ nee bɛ gɔnwo mɔ ɛlɛdie bɛ nye anzɛɛ bɛlɛkɔ bɛabɔ bɔlo a , bɛ nuhua ko nea kɛ ɔbava Daniel yeaboka nwo . ”
Ɛnɛ ɔ nee ye mame ɛlɛbɔ mɔdenle kpalɛ .
Nɔhalɛ nu , yɛlɛ ndenle dɔɔnwo mɔɔ yɛbahola yɛalua zo yɛaboa na yɛakyekye bɛdabɛ mɔɔ bɛsu la arɛle .
Eza Baebolo ne ka kenle bie anyelazo mɔɔ yɛ anyelielɛ la anwo edwɛkɛ fa kyekye yɛ rɛle .
Bie mɔ kɛlɛ kenle mɔɔ ahenle wule la wɔ bɛ kalenda zo mɔɔ ɔkakye bɛ mekɛ mɔɔ bɛfa bɛkyekye awie arɛle , wɔ kenle zɔhane anzɛɛ ɔka ekyii na kenle ne adwu a .
Bie a ɛbahakye kɛ Gail , mɔɔ yɛlimoa yɛha ɔ nwo edwɛkɛ la adwenle nu yɛle ye kesee kɛ saa ɔbahola yeagyinla ɔ hu , Rob ewule ne anloa a .
Noko akee , ɔ nye la kɛ ɔbanwu ye bieko wɔ ewiade fofolɛ ne mɔɔ Nyamenle ɛbɔ nwolɛ ɛwɔkɛ la anu .
Medi bɛdabɛ mɔɔ bɛ kulovolɛ bie ɛwu noko bɛnze anyelazo ɛhye kɛ bɛbanwu bɛ bieko la anwo nyane . ”
Ɔnrɛhyɛ , Nyamenle bayɛ ye zɔ yeamaa Dwobu nee menli dɔɔnwo wɔ mekɛ mɔɔ azɛlɛ ɛhye bahakyi paladaese la .
Baebolo ne ka ye wɔ Gyima ne 24 : 15 kɛ , ‘ Menli badwazo ara ngoane nu . ’
Gyisɛse hanle kɛ , “ Bɛmmamaa ɛhye yɛ bɛ azibɛnwo ; mekɛ ɛlɛba mɔɔ mɔwuamra amuala bade ɔ ne wɔ bɛ nla ne mɔ anu , na bɛvi bɛ nla ne mɔ anu bɛbavinde . ”
Ɔbanyia “ ye mgbavolɛ nu anwosesebɛ ” ne bieko na ye nwonane ne ‘ azia ayɛ kɛ ye mgbavolɛ ’ nu ɛdeɛ ne dahuu .
( Dwobu 33 : 24 , 25 ) Bɛbayɛ zɔhane ala bɛamaa bɛdabɛ mɔɔ bɛkile anyezɔlɛ wɔ Nyamenle anwunvɔnezelɛ nziezielɛ ne mɔɔ fale azɛlɛ ye azo ewudwazo ne anwo la .
Saa wɔli nyane wɔ wɔ kulovolɛ bie ewule nwo a , edwɛkɛ mɔɔ yɛzuzu nwo la ɛnrɛye wɔ nyane ne ɛnrɛvi ɛkɛ ne bɔkɔɔ .
Saa ɛdwenledwenle Nyamenle ɛwɔkɛ ne mɔ anwo a , ɛbanyia anyelazo nee anwosesebɛ mɔɔ baboa wɔ a . ​ — 1 Tɛsalonaekama 4 : 13 .
Ɛkulo kɛ ɛsukoa dɔɔnwo ɛfale kɛzi ɛbagyinla nyanelilɛ nloa la ɔ ?
Anzɛɛ ɛbahola wɔazuzu kpuya mɔɔ le kɛ “ Duzu ati a Nyamenle maa ɛtaneyɛlɛ nee amaneɛnwunlɛ nwo adenle a ? ”
Yɛsɛlɛ wɔ , kɔ yɛ wɛbsaete , jw.org ne azo na nwu kɛzi Baebolo ne maa yɛ arɛlekyekyelɛ nwo mualɛ kpalɛ la .
‘ Nyamenle bakyikyi bɛ nye anwo monle . Ewule ɛnle ɛkɛ bieko . ’ ​ — Yekile 21 : 3 , 4 .
Ɛzinzalɛ Arane ɛhye baha kɛzi Nyamenle bamaa ɛwɔkɛ ɛhye ara nu nee mɔɔ ɔbahile yeamaa wɔ la anwo edwɛkɛ .
EDWƐKƐ TITILI | DUZU ATI A GYISƐSE NWUNLE AMANEƐ NA ƆWULE A ?
Wɔ 33 Y.M . nyenyesuo mekɛ nu , bɛhunle Gyisɛse mɔɔ vi Nazalɛte la .
Bɛdole ye ɛzonle kɛ ɔle maamɔvo , bɛbole ye atisesebɛ nu na bɛbɔle ye baka nu .
Noko Nyamenle dwazole Gyisɛse rale ngoane nu , na ye kenle 40 anzi , ɔhɔle anwuma .
Yɛnwu nwanwane edwɛkɛ ɛhye wɔ Edwɛkpa nna ne mɔɔ wɔ Kilisiene Giliki Ngɛlɛlera ne , mɔɔ bɛta bɛfɛlɛ ye Ngyekyeleɛ Fofolɛ ne la anu .
Wɔ adenle fofolɛ zo , saa edwɛkɛ ɛhye mɔ zile a ɛnee alesama lɛ kenle bie anyelazo kpalɛ , mɔɔ ɛbahola wɔaboka nwo a .
Yemɔti , Edwɛkpa ne le nɔhalɛ anzɛɛ ɔle nwɔra ɔ ?
Edwɛkpa ne ɛnle kɛ nwɔra mɔɔ bɛbɔ bɛ ti anu bɛto la , ɔka edwɛkɛ ne pɛpɛɛpɛ na ɔtwe adwenle ɔsie edwɛkɛ fɔɔnwo bie azo .
Kɛ neazo la , azua aluma wɔ nu mɔɔ bɛ nuhua dɔɔnwo wɔ ɛkɛ mɔɔ ɛbahola wɔahɔ ɛkɛ ɛnɛ a .
Bɛka menli mɔɔ bɛdɛnlanle aze mɔɔ tetedwɛkɛ kɛlɛvoma ɛlie ɛdo nu kɛ ɔle zɔ la anwo edwɛkɛ . ​ — Luku 3 : 1 , 2 , 23 .
Ewiade kɛlɛvoma mɔɔ dɛnlanle aze wɔ ɛvoya mɔɔ limoa nee mɔɔ tɔ zo nwiɔ anu la hanle Gyisɛse anwo edwɛkɛ .
* Adenle mɔɔ bɛluale zo bɛhunle ye , mɔɔ bɛha ye wɔ Edwɛkpa ne anu la nee adenle mɔɔ Wulomuma dua zo ku menli wɔ mekɛ zɔhane la le ko .
Bieko , bɛka edwɛkɛ ne nɔhalɛ nu , bɔbɔ bɛhanle Gyisɛse ɛdoavolɛma ne nyɛleɛ bie mɔ mɔɔ ɛnle kpalɛ la anwo edwɛkɛ .
Edwɛkɛ ɛhye mɔ amuala di daselɛ kɛ Edwɛkpa kɛlɛvoma ne le nɔhavoma na mɔɔ bɛhɛlɛle wɔ Gyisɛse anwo la le pɛpɛɛpɛ .
Menli dɔɔnwo die di kɛ Gyisɛse dɛnlanle aze na ɔwule ɛdeɛ , noko bie mɔ su ye ewudwazo ne anwo kpolera .
Ye ɛzoanvolɛma ne bɔbɔ anlie anli wɔ mekɛ mɔɔ limoa mɔɔ bɛdele kɛ yedwazo la .
Noko mekɛ mɔɔ bɛ nee ɛdoavolɛma gyɛne nwunle ye wɔ ɛleka ngakyile la bɛliele bɛlile .
Nɔhalɛ nu , mekɛ bie anu , menli mɔɔ bo 500 la nwunle ye . ​ — 1 Kɔlentema 15 : 6 .
Ɛdoavolɛma ne vale akɛnrasesebɛ bɔle Gyisɛse ewudwazo ne anwo nolo hilele awie biala ​ — bɔbɔ bɛdabɛ mɔɔ bɛhunle ye la , ɔnva nwo kɛ ɛnee bɛkola bɛkye bɛ na bɛku bɛ la .
Saa ɛnee ɛdoavolɛma ne ɛnlie ɛnli kɛ bɛdwazole Gyisɛse amgba a , asoo anrɛɛ bɛbanyia akɛnrasesebɛ ɔ ?
Nɔhalɛ nu , Gyisɛse ewudwazo ne mɔɔ zile amgba la a le debie mɔɔ Kilisiene ɛzonlenlɛ ne gyi zo ɔvi mekɛ zɔhane dedee badwu ɛnɛ .
Gyisɛse ewule nee ye ewudwazo ne anwo kɛlɛtokɛ mɔɔ wɔ ɛkɛ la di daselɛ kɛ Edwɛkpa ne le nɔhalɛ wɔ tetedwɛkɛ nu .
Saa ɛtɔ ɛ rɛle aze ɛkenga a ɔbamaa wɔanyia anwodozo kɛ edwɛkɛ ɛhye mɔ sisile amgba .
Saa ɛte deɛmɔti bɛzile la abo a , wɔ anwodozo ne bayɛ kpole .
Tacitus mɔɔ bɛwole ye kɛyɛ 55 Y.M . anu , hɛlɛle kɛ “ Kelaese mɔɔ ye nuhua a [ Kilisienema ] nyianle bɛ duma ne vile la , nwunle amaneɛ kpole wɔ Pɔnteɛse Paelɛte asa nu wɔ mekɛ mɔɔ amɛnlado Taebileɛse ɛlɛdi tumi la . ”
Suetonius ( ɛvoya mɔɔ limoa ) ; Dwuuma tetedwɛkɛ kɛlɛvo Josephus ( ɛvoya mɔɔ limoa ) yɛɛ Pliny , Baetenea amɛnlado Kpavolɛ ne ( ɛvoya mɔɔ tɔ zo nwiɔ la mɔlebɛbo ) noko hanle Gyisɛse anwo edwɛkɛ .
Bieko , ɔbayɛ se kɛ Gyisɛse kpɔvolɛma ne bɛahɛlɛ edwɛkɛ mɔɔ baboa menli yeamaa bɛalie Gyisɛse bɛali la .
Ɛzoanvolɛ Pita hanle Gyisɛse ewudwazo ne anwo edwɛkɛ kɛ : “ Na ye kenle nsa ne azo Nyamenle dwazole ye vile mɔwuamra anu na ɔmanle ɔyele ɔ nwo ɔhilele yɛmɛ mɔɔ Nyamenle ɛye yɛ kɛ yɛli daselɛ la [ na tɛ menli kɔsɔɔti ɔ , NW ] . Yɛ nee ye lile , nlonle , wɔ mekɛ mɔɔ ɔdwazole ɔvile ewule nu la . ”
Mateyu Edwɛkpa ne ka kile yɛ kɛ mekɛ mɔɔ ɛzonlenlɛ nu agbɔvolɛ dele Gyisɛse ewudwazo ne anwo edwɛkɛ la , bɛbɔle adwenle kɛ bɛpe adenle bie azo bɛadua bɛ amaa menli ande . ​ — Mateyu 28 : 11 - 15 .
Asoo ɛhye kile kɛ ɛnee Gyisɛse kulo kɛ bɛfea ye ewudwazo ne anwo edwɛkɛ ne azo ɔ ?
Kyɛkyɛ , Pita doale zo kɛ : “ Ɔzele yɛ kɛ yɛha ɔ nwo Edwɛkpa ne yɛhile menli kɔsɔɔti , na yɛli ɔ nwo daselɛ kɛ yemɔ yɛɛ Nyamenle ɛyɛ ye mɔwuamra nee anyewɔzoamra ndɛnebuavolɛ a . ”
Nɔhalɛ Kilisienema ɛyɛ ye zɔ na bɛtɛkɔ zo bɛtɛyɛ . ​ — Gyima ne 10 : 42 .
“ Ɛtane luale sonla ko [ Adam ] anwo zo a rale ewiade , na sonla ko ne ɛtane ne vale ewule rale . ” ​ — Wulomuma 5 : 12
Saa bɛbiza wɔ kɛ , “ Ɛkulo kɛ ɛtɛnla aze dahuu ɔ ? ” Duzu a ɛbaha a ?
Bie a , menli dɔɔnwo baha kɛ bɛkulo kɛ bɛtɛnla aze noko bɛte nganeɛ kɛ ɔnrɛyɛ boɛ , yemɔti ɔnle kɛ bɛdwenle nwo .
Bɛka kɛ saa yɛnwu a anrɛɛ ɔnle kpalɛ , ɔle yɛ ɛbɛlabɔlɛ ne awieleɛ .
Noko , saa bɛbiza wɔ wɔ adenle fofolɛ zo kɛ , “ Ɛkulo kɛ ɛwu ɔ ? ”
Ye biala anu , menli dɔɔnwo babua kɛ kyɛkyɛ .
Baebolo ne kilehile kɛ Nyamenle bɔle alesama kɛ bɛdɛnla aze dahuu .
Nɔhalɛ nu , ɔse “ yeva mɔɔ ɛnlɛ awieleɛ yewula sonla adwenle nu . ” ​ — Nolobɔvo ne 3 : 11 .
Noko , nɔhalɛ ne a le kɛ alesama ɛndɛnla aze dahuu .
Bieko , asoo Nyamenle ɛyɛ tɛnlabelɛ ne anwo debie ɔ ?
Baebolo ne mualɛ ne maa anwosesebɛ , na bɛmaa yɛnwu deɛmɔti Gyisɛse nwunle amaneɛ na ɔwule la .
Mɔlebɛbo buluku ne tile nsa mɔɔ limoa la ka kɛ Nyamenle vale dahuu ngoane anyelazo nee mɔɔ Adam nee Yevi yɛ a bɛ sa baha ye la ziele bɛ nyunlu .
Akee edwɛkɛ ne maa yɛnwu kɛzi bɛandie Nyamenle na anyelazo ɛhye bɔle bɛ la .
Bɛha edwɛkɛ ne sikalɛ , mɔɔ maa bie mɔ bu ye kɛ asɛɛ ɔle nwɔra ala .
Noko Mɔlebɛbo buluku ne maa yɛnwu kɛ kɛlɛtokɛ ne le tetedwɛkɛ mɔɔ le nɔhalɛ , kɛ mɔɔ Edwɛkpa ne mɔ de la .
Duzu a ɛvi Adam anzosesebɛ ne anu ɛra a ?
Baebolo ne bua kɛ : “ Ɛtane luale sonla ko [ Adam ] anwo zo a rale ewiade , na sonla ko ne ɛtane ne vale ewule rale la , yɛɛ ewule dele kpondenle aleɛabo amra anwo zo a , ɔluakɛ menli kɔsɔɔti ɛyɛ ɛtane . ”
Yemɔti , dahuu ngoane anyelazo ne bɔle ye na awieleɛ ne ɔwule .
Kɛmɔ yɛle ɔ bo zo amra la ati , yeva ɛtane ne yewo yɛ .
Noko asoo Nyamenle ɛyɛ tɛnlabelɛ ne anwo debie ɔ ?
Nyamenle yɛle ngyehyɛleɛ kɛ ɔdie anzɛɛ ɔtɔ dahuu ngoane ne mɔɔ Adam ɛmaa yebɔ ɔ bo zo amra la .
Baebolo ne ka ye wɔ Wulomuma 6 : 23 kɛ , “ Ɛtane ahatualɛ a le ewule . ”
Ɛhye kile kɛ ɛtane a maa yɛwu a .
Zɔhane ala a , yɛyɛ ɛtane na yɛwu yɛtua yɛ ɛtane ne anwo kakɛ a .
Noko bɛwole yɛ wɔ ɛtane nu mɔɔ tɛ yɛdayɛ a yɛyɛle a .
Yemɔti Nyamenle vile ɛlɔlɛ nu zoanle ɔ Ra , Gyisɛse kɛ ɔradua yɛ ‘ ɛtane nwo kakɛ ’ ne ɔmaa yɛ .
Gyisɛse ewule ne ɛbuke dahuu ngoane nwo adenle mɔɔ yɛ anyelielɛ la ɛmaa yɛ
Kɛ mɔɔ Adam mɔɔ di munli la luale anzosesebɛ zo vale ɛtane nee ewule rale yɛ nwo zo la , zɔhane ala a yɛhyia sonla mɔɔ di munli , mɔɔ bayɛ tieyɛ ahɔdwu ewule nu la amaa yealie yɛ yeavi ɛtane nu a .
Baebolo ne ka kɛ : “ Kɛmɔ sonla ko anzosesebɛ ti menli muala yɛle ɛtanevolɛma la , zɔhane ala yɛɛ ɔlua sonla ko anzomɛlɛkɛ zo menli somaa bazɔ Nyamenle anye a . ”
Ɔvile anwuma lɔ ɔrayɛle sonla mɔɔ di munli * , na ɔrawule ɔmaanle yɛ .
Ɛhye ati , yɛnyia gyinlabelɛ kpalɛ wɔ Nyamenle anyunlu na yɛnyia dahuu ngoane anyelazo .
Noko , nzɔne ati a ɛnee ɔwɔ kɛ Gyisɛse wu na yeahola yeayɛ ɛhye ɛ ?
Asoo anrɛɛ Tumivolɛ Bedevinli Nyamenle ne ɛnrɛhola ɛnrɛha ye sikalɛ kɛ Adam abozoamra bahola adɛnla aze dahuu ɔ ?
Saa Nyamenle bule ɔ nye guale pɛlepɛlelilɛ zo wɔ edwɛkɛ ɛhye anu a , anrɛɛ menli ɛnrɛnwu mɔɔ ɔbayɛ ye wɔ edwɛkɛ gyɛne nu la .
Kɛ neazo la , asoo anrɛɛ ɔbali pɛlepɛle wɔ awie mɔɔ ɔfɛta kɛ ɔnyia ngoane wɔ Adam abozoamra anu la ɔ ?
Asoo anrɛɛ bɛbalie ye bɛali kɛ ɔdi ye ɛwɔkɛ zo ɔ ?
Pɛlepɛlelilɛ mɔɔ Nyamenle vale lile gyima liele yɛ ngoane la maa yɛnyia anwodozo kɛ ɔbayɛ mɔɔ tenrɛ la dahuu .
Nyamenle ɛlua Gyisɛse ewule ne azo ɛmaa yɛnyia dahuu ngoane nwo anyelazo wɔ azɛlɛ ye azo Paladaese ne anu .
Yɛ Gyisɛse edwɛkɛ mɔɔ wɔ Dwɔn 3 : 16 la nzonlɛ : “ Nyamenle hulole ewiade amra kpole kpalɛ la ati yɛɛ ɔvale Ɔ Ra kokye ne ɔmanle a , amaa awie biala mɔɔ kɛlie ye kɛli la anwu na yeanyia ngoane mɔɔ ɛnlɛ awieleɛ . ”
Yemɔti Gyisɛse ewule ne le debie mɔɔ maa yɛnwu kɛ Nyamenle di pɛlepɛle yɛɛ ye titili ne , ye ɛlɔlɛ kpole mɔɔ ɔlɛ ɔmaa alesama la .
Noko , duzu ati a ɛnee ɔwɔ kɛ Gyisɛse nwu amaneɛ na ɔwu nyane ewule kɛ mɔɔ Edwɛkpa ne mɔ hanle la ɛ ?
Sɔnea kpole ɛhye anloa mɔɔ Gyisɛse gyinlanle na ɔlile nɔhalɛ la kile kɛ yemaa Abɔnsam edwɛkɛ ne mɔɔ ɔhanle kɛ alesama ɛnrɛli nɔhalɛ ɛnrɛmaa Nyamenle wɔ ngyegyelɛ mekɛ nu la ɛyɛ adalɛ .
( Dwobu 2 : 4 , 5 ) Ɔzɔho kɛ Seetan edwɛkɛ ɛhye yɛle nɔhalɛ wɔ mekɛ mɔɔ ɔbɛlɛbɛlale Adam mɔɔ di munli ɔmaanle ɔyɛle ɛtane la .
Noko Gyisɛse mɔɔ ɛnee di munli kɛ Adam la lile nɔhalɛ ɔnva nwo kɛ ɔnwunle amaneɛ kpole la .
Ɔhilele kɛ anrɛɛ Adam noko bahola azi kpɔkɛ adie Nyamenle .
Gyisɛse maanle yɛ ndonwo kɛ yɛli ɔ nzi ɔlua sɔnea mɔɔ ɔgyinlanle ɔ nloa la azo .
Nyamenle ɛyila ɔ Ra , Gyisɛse wɔ ye tieyɛ ne anwo , yemaa ye damɛnlangoate ngoane wɔ anwuma .
Gyisɛse hanle mɔɔ ɔwɔ kɛ yɛyɛ la , ɔse : “ Ngoane mɔɔ ɛnlɛ awieleɛ la a le kɛ bɛkɛnwu kɛ wɔmɔ a ɛle nɔhalɛ Nyamenle kokye ne a , na bɛkɛnwu Gyisɛse Kelaese , mɔɔ wɔzoa ye la . ” ​ — Dwɔn 17 : 3 .
