Nea edwɛkɛ mɔɔ se “ Ɛnee Yidɛn Tola Bie Wɔ Ɛkɛ Amgba Ɔ ? , ” mɔɔ wɔ February 1 , 2011 , Ɛzinzalɛ Arane ne mukelɛ 4 - 9 mɔɔ Gyihova Alasevolɛ ɛyɛ la anu .
Nyamenle Ara ne mɔɔ ɔyele ye ngoane ɔvile anwuma ɔwulale Mɛle awodeɛ nu la maanle ɔnrenzɛle , na Nyamenle sunsum ne bɔle Gyisɛse anwo bane amaa yeanyia sinlidɔlɛ biala . ​ — Luku 1 : 31 , 35 .
Nɔe ne mɔɔ aleɛ kye a Gyisɛse bawu la , ɔyiale ye ɛzoanvolɛ nɔhavoma ne na ɔvale ye ewule ne anwo Ngakyelɛ ɔziele ɛkɛ .
Ɔzele bɛ kɛ : “ Anrɛɛ bɛyɛ ɛhye bɛva bɛhakye me . ”
Ɛvolɛ biala , Gyihova Alasevolɛ mɔɔ wɔ ewiade amuala la yia nu kakye Gyisɛse ewule ne fa di ye edwɛkɛ ne azo .
Wɔ ɛvolɛ ɛhye anu , Ngakyelɛlilɛ ne bazi Maanle , March 23 , mekɛ mɔɔ ewia ne ɛhɔdɔ la .
Awie biala kola ba bie ; bɛnlielie ezukoa wɔ ɛkɛ .
Yɛsɛlɛ wɔ biza Gyihova Alasevolɛ mɔɔ wɔ wɔ ɛkɛ ne la maa bɛhile wɔ mekɛ nee ɛleka ne .
