Adiema raalɛ ko vale The Harp of God , buluku mɔɔ gyi Baebolo ne azo la bie maanle yɛ .
Kɛ kpavolɛ la , ɛnee ɔyɛ me fɛ kɛ mebalua Nyamenle Edwɛkɛ ne azo meamaa menli anyia anyelazo .
Adiema kpanyinli ne maanle yɛgyinlanle , na ɔhanle kɛ memaa yɛdɛnla baka bie mɔɔ la ɛkɛ la azo .
Ɔhanle kɛ : “ Nwane a maanle wɔ tumi kɛ ɛbua awie ndɛne kɛ ɔle abɔnkye a ?
Maa yɛva anyelielɛ yɛha edwɛkpa ne na yɛgyakyi ndɛnebualɛ ne yɛmaa Gyihova . ”
Adiema kpanyinli ko noko hanle kɛ , saa ɛmaanlɛ bamaa me nye alie a , ɔwɔ kɛ mesi abotane .
Wɔ ɛvolɛ dɔɔnwo anzi , ɔnyianle ye abotane ne azo nvasoɛ wɔ mekɛ mɔɔ bɛzɔnenle ɔ ye kɛ Gyihova Dasevolɛ la .
Wɔ konle ne anzi , menyɛle adekpakyelɛ gyima ne ɛvolɛ nwiɔ wɔ Ireland nyiakɛ .
Ɛnee yɛnze kɛ ɛsɔfo ne mɔ a lɛ tumi kpalɛ wɔ maanle ne anu a .
Ɛnee metɛfale meli metɛtule adenle ɛlɛ , yemɔti me nye liele kpalɛ .
Yɛvale ɛvolɛ nnu yɛhanle edwɛkɛ ne wɔ mbɔra mɔɔ bɛde bɛ nwo na Alasevolɛ ɛnle ɛkɛ la azo .
Edwɛkpatɛlɛvolɛma mɔɔ ɛnee wɔ Sibia ne anu la ( bɛne zo kɔ fema zo ) : Ron Parkin , Dick Ryde , Gust Maki , yɛɛ Stanley Carter
Bɛta bɛmaa yɛ fɛlɛ amolɛ , avoka nee ahule .
